, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Duloxetine, Isocarboxazid, Viloxazine, Esketamine, More', 'Potassium bicarbonate, Potassium gluconate', 1767369485);
